--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
国土数値情報 鉄道時系列データ (N02) / National Land Numerical Information
https://nlftp.mlit.go.jp/ksj/gml/datalist/KsjTmplt-N02.html
License: 政府標準利用規約 (第2.0版) / Government of Japan Standard Terms of Use 2.0
https://www.digital.go.jp/resources/data_policy
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This product includes data derived from "国土数値情報（鉄道時系列データ）"
provided by 国土交通省 (Ministry of Land, Infrastructure, Transport and
Tourism, Japan).

出典: 「国土数値情報（鉄道時系列データ）」(国土交通省) を加工して作成
Source: "National Land Numerical Information (Railway Time Series Data)"
        (MLIT, Japan), processed by the project owner.

加工内容 (Processing applied):
- rail_lines.json: N02 railway segment data filtered to the Kansai 6-prefecture
  area (大阪府/兵庫県/京都府/奈良県/滋賀県/和歌山県), aggregated by operator
  and line name. JR West Tokaido Line is split into three logical sections
  by longitude thresholds: (米原〜京都), (京都〜大阪), (大阪〜姫路).
- rail_stations.json: N02 station data filtered to the same area, with the
  same regional labelling applied to Tokaido Line stations.

The processed JSON files are distributed in this repository for convenience
and remain subject to the Government of Japan Standard Terms of Use 2.0.

